  <Docs>
    <summary>
            An event source logger for SDK messages that integrates with System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.
            </summary>
    <remarks>
            This logger provides the C# idiomatic EventSource logging support for the Speech SDK,
            enabling integration with .NET diagnostics tools such as PerfView, Application Insights,
            and other EventSource consumers.
            Note that EventSource logging is a process-wide construct. If multiple speech recognizer
            instances are running in parallel, their events will be interleaved in the log output.
            The EventSource name used by this logger is "Microsoft-CognitiveServices-Speech".
            </remarks>
  </Docs>
